  "critical_note": "Master enabler: every later stage depends on precision parts — cylinders, leadscrews, slides, seals",
  "description": "Precision manufacturing capability built via Gingery-style iterative bootstrap: casting → crude lathe → improved lathe → shaper → mill → drill press → surface grinder. Covers metal forming, machining, joining, and casting. The single most important parallel track — without machine tools, no semiconductor equipment can be built.",
